      • getVariableDeclarationNamesFromTokens

        public List<IToken> getVariableDeclarationNamesFromTokens(List<IToken> variableDeclarationTokens)
        Returns all variable names from the given variable declaration tokens. Names are only returned if they are newly introduced, that means, that e. g. the variable "t" from "using(t) {" will not be returned. This method does not support generic types at the moment.
